    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/d24e6fb0ee44dec95d7b28facb7ebb44.avif?t=1756206184\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Sa[meow]rai：银翼喵侍》是一款以一击必杀和丰富互动性为核心的俯视角动作冒险游戏，你将体验到极具冲击力的未来风格视觉效果与血浆四溅的刺激战斗。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >施展居合斩与弹反，在穷凶极恶的敌人之间周旋，为自己争取生存的每一秒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/0b6fb7d57ef027e6642b4b91e9dc513b.poster.avif?t=1756206184\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/0b6fb7d57ef027e6642b4b91e9dc513b.webm?t=1756206184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/0b6fb7d57ef027e6642b4b91e9dc513b.mp4?t=1756206184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或是利用你手中一切可用工具，操纵场景中的电子设备与机关，创造出对你有利的局面。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/6cd7b2d8adeee4045e2c31873d4bdda3.poster.avif?t=1756206184\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/6cd7b2d8adeee4045e2c31873d4bdda3.webm?t=1756206184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/6cd7b2d8adeee4045e2c31873d4bdda3.mp4?t=1756206184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/048b1ce3da1ac3786245c5cd6d0d7590.avif?t=1756206184\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内穿插手绘漫画过场动画，讲述了一个被往事与悔恨缠绕的赛博义警，踏上一条惊心动魄且无人理解的复仇之路的故事。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/84e8cb8ab87e53c2f5393ae5c5fa2119.poster.avif?t=1756206184\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/84e8cb8ab87e53c2f5393ae5c5fa2119.webm?t=1756206184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/84e8cb8ab87e53c2f5393ae5c5fa2119.mp4?t=1756206184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个阴谋丛生的未来大都市，警方与企业的战争一触即发，你将能够与大量特征各异、富有魅力的角色发生故事。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助他们实现愿望，或是背叛他们达成目的？大量的剧情分支与隐藏剧情由你来选择。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/4733ce930594e956281f30cd19cf7a26.poster.avif?t=1756206184\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/4733ce930594e956281f30cd19cf7a26.webm?t=1756206184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/4733ce930594e956281f30cd19cf7a26.mp4?t=1756206184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿梭在战争与阴谋中的三教九流们都使用什么样的武器？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随剧情与各路角色的指引，找到那些隐藏在各处的传说武器！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/79f1a4d92bcbfdb08980080a31a97694.poster.avif?t=1756206184\" width=1600 height=900 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/79f1a4d92bcbfdb08980080a31a97694.webm?t=1756206184\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/79f1a4d92bcbfdb08980080a31a97694.mp4?t=1756206184\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/03029522dfc1a8bd4d13452e2bf4df2b.avif?t=1756206184\" width=616 height=143 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当往事留下的痕迹如此生动而鲜活，现实却满是悔恨与一地血污。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此时“回到过去”的计划被推到桌上，你是否会不顾一切抓住那渺茫的希望？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是任凭一切消逝，走向一个无人知晓的未来？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于制作组</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狗红工作室是一家致力于将独特的视觉风格与现代设计思路相结合，开发出令玩家印象深刻的作品的独立游戏工作室。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于发行商</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GCORES PUBLISHING 是由机核组建的独立游戏发行业务，未来也将不断带给大家 BOOOM暴造 创作活动中的优秀独立游戏。欢迎关注我们的发行商页面。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于BOOOM暴造</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机核网旗下的独立游戏品牌。「BOOOMJAM 游戏创作挑战」是每年固定举办2次，限时开发三周、限定开发主题的游戏创作活动。在开发阶段结束后，面向所有玩家举办线上试玩游戏节，以及在机核的大型线下电子游戏嘉年华上对这些游戏进行展示。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119690/extras/ee65c707057721ab09cbfa632da86d47.avif?t=1756206184\" width=587 height=71 /></span></p>",
